				<p class="text-xs font-mono text-teal mb-3 mt-8">how it all connects</p>
				<p class="mb-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
					One of the best parts of running a homelab is replacing SaaS dependencies with self-hosted
					alternatives that integrate with each other. I set up <a
						href="/blog/adding-custom-domain-names-on-your-internal-network-using-nginx-proxy-manager-and-pi-hole/"
						class="text-coral hover:text-teal"
						>custom domain names with Nginx Proxy Manager and Pi-hole</a
					> so every service gets a clean local URL.
